@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

title FIG-04-05. Horizon Bank Payment Validation Activity Diagram

|Payments Platform|
start
:Receive payment instruction;
:Validate mandatory fields;
:Check payment limits;

|Financial Crime Platform|
:Screen payment instruction;

|Payments Platform|
if (Checks passed?) then ([valid and clear])
  :Accept payment for posting;
  :Record accepted status;
else ([invalid or screened out])
  :Reject payment instruction;
  :Record rejected status;
endif

stop

legend right
  Guards label the decision paths.
  Swimlanes show responsibility, not deployment.
endlegend
@enduml
